String.name: Substantial Enchantment Blessing
String.tooltip: Your enchantment chance is substantially increased. Applies to items of all tiers, but only up to enchantment level +12.

String.name: Greater Enchantment Blessing
String.tooltip: Your enchantment chance is greatly increased. Applies to items of all tiers, but only up to enchantment level +12.

String.name: Massive Enchantment Blessing
String.tooltip: Your enchantment chance is massively increased. Applies to items of all tiers, but only up to enchantment level +12.
